                                <a href="/kashmirialphabetcharts/" class="overlay-download-link">
                                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                        <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path>
                                        <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline>
                                        <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line>
                                    </svg>
                                    Explore More
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="resource-item-content">
                            <h3 class="resource-item-title">Kashmiri Alphabet Chart</h3>
                            <p class="resource-item-desc">This chart brings together the plants and animals of Kashmir - from kingfishers to willow trees to spiders and langurs—all through the English alphabet.</p>
                            <div class="resource-item-footer">
                                <a href="/kashmirialphabetcharts/" class="single-download-btn" style="background: var(--resources-primary); color: #fff; text-align: center;">
                                    Explore More →
