                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="resource-item-content">
                            <h3 class="resource-item-title">Tamil Alphabet Chart</h3>
                            <p class="resource-item-desc">This chart brings together the plants and animals of Tamil Nadu, from dugongs to Indrella snails, fungi, odonates, wasps, and wildflowers, all through the Tamil alphabet.</p>
                            <div class="resource-item-footer">
                                <a href="/tamilalphabetcharts/" class="single-download-btn" style="background: var(--resources-primary); color: #fff; text-align: center;">
